# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:9
translate spanish dana0_4b30accf:

    # "I decide to go back inside the office and chat with Dana a little bit more. I turn off the car and walk back into the building."
    "Decido volver a entrar en la oficina y charlar un rato más con Dana. Apago el coche y vuelvo al edificio."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:11
translate spanish dana0_bfd0c735:

    # cw "Oh hey, did you forget something?"
    cw "Oh, hola, ¿te has olvidado algo?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:12
translate spanish dana0_003419c5:

    # pc "No, I just wanted to come in and chat for a bit."
    pc "No, solo quería entrar a charlar un rato."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:14
translate spanish dana0_928517bb:

    # cw "Oh, with me?"
    cw "Oh, ¿conmigo?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:15
translate spanish dana0_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:17
translate spanish dana0_cce31900:

    # "Dana's face grows a bit red."
    "A Dana se le sonroja un poco la cara."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:18
translate spanish dana0_bb093f6c:

    # cw "Oh, well I'm kind of busy right now. I have to organize all this stuff before I can go home, and I have to be home at seven."
    cw "Oh, bueno, ahora mismo estoy un poco ocupada. Tengo que organizar todo esto antes de poder irme a casa, y tengo que estar en casa a las siete."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:22
translate spanish dana0_356ae111:

    # cw "You would do that? Sure, pull up a chair."
    cw "¿Lo harías? Claro, acerca una silla."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:26
translate spanish dana0_8dbdc8d1:

    # cw "No problem. See you Monday."
    cw "No hay problema. Nos vemos el lunes."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:29
translate spanish dana0_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/dana_seeyoutomorrow.mp3"
    voice "voices/dana_seeyoutomorrow.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:30
translate spanish dana0_9da3accd:

    # cw "No problem. See you tomorrow."
    cw "No hay problema. Nos vemos mañana."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:31
translate spanish dana0_e8e6d974:

    # "I head back to the car and leave."
    "Vuelvo al coche y me voy."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:36
translate spanish dana0_b791cdf1:

    # "I take one of the chairs and pull it over next to her. I spend the next hour going through the stacks of paper on her desk and sorting them by date."
    "Cojo una de las sillas y la acerco a ella. Me paso la siguiente hora revisando las pilas de papeles de su escritorio y ordenándolas por fecha."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:37
translate spanish dana0_34290a3e:

    # "It is easy work and Dana is good company. We don't talk much, but every time I catch her eye, she is smiling."
    "Es un trabajo fácil y Dana es buena compañía. No hablamos mucho, pero cada vez que cruzo la mirada con ella, me sonríe."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:38
translate spanish dana0_2dbc8990:

    # "We finish just before seven."
    "Terminamos justo antes de las siete."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:41
translate spanish dana0_02cb5af0:

    # cw "Oh my God, thank you so much for helping me. There's no way I would've finished it in time if you weren't here."
    cw "Dios mío, muchísimas gracias por ayudarme. No habría podido terminarlo a tiempo si no hubieras estado aquí."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:42
translate spanish dana0_a7c1d064:

    # pc "No problem. Glad to help."
    pc "No hay problema. Me alegro de haberte ayudado."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:43
translate spanish dana0_3a92acde:

    # cw "You're the best. I have to run though, so I'll see you later, okay?"
    cw "Eres el mejor. Pero tengo que irme corriendo, así que nos vemos luego, ¿vale?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:44
translate spanish dana0_82f4d7ef:

    # "I don't really want to say goodbye to her, and I get a sudden burst of courage."
    "La verdad es que no quiero despedirme de ella, y de repente me entra un arrebato de valor."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:45
translate spanish dana0_4005f1c2:

    # pc "I'm kind of hungry. Want to grab a bite to eat somewhere?"
    pc "Tengo un poco de hambre. ¿Te apetece ir a comer algo?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:47
translate spanish dana0_a9645bb5:

    # "Her smile fades away a bit."
    "Su sonrisa se desvanece un poco."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:49
translate spanish dana0_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/dana_sortofengaged.mp3"
    voice "voices/dana_sortofengaged.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:50
translate spanish dana0_92e7ded7:

    # cw "I'm not sure that's a good idea. I'm sort of engaged. I don't think he'd like to see me talking to other guys outside of work."
    cw "No sé si es buena idea. Estoy más o menos comprometida. No creo que a él le gustara verme hablando con otros chicos fuera del trabajo."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:51
translate spanish dana0_1dad11d2:

    # pc "Oh, I'm sorry. I didn't mean to make you feel uncomfortable."
    pc "Oh, lo siento. No era mi intención hacerte sentir incómoda."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:53
translate spanish dana0_094901ac:

    # voice dana_seeyoulater
    # cw "It's okay. I'll see you later, okay?"
    voice dana_seeyoulater
    cw ""

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:57
translate spanish dana0_437e96ea:

    # "She smiles and guides me out the front door so that she can start closing up the office."
    "Ella sonríe y me acompaña hasta la puerta principal para poder empezar a cerrar la oficina."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:58
translate spanish dana0_7679afbc:

    # "Struck out. Oops. Maybe I shouldn't have pushed it? Oh well."
    "Me ha salido mal. Vaya. ¿Quizás no debería haber insistido? Bueno, da igual."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:59
translate spanish dana0_75b9bff6:

    # "I head back to the car."
    "Vuelvo al coche."

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:1
    old "Dana needs some help with her paperwork after work."
    new "Dana necesita ayuda con el papeleo después del trabajo."

    # game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:2
    old "You could help her any weekday evening after you finish work."
    new "Podrías ayudarla cualquier tarde entre semana después de terminar de trabajar."

    # game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:20
    old "Maybe I could help you sort?"
    new "¿Quizás podría ayudarte a ordenarlo?"

    # game/Scenes/Dana/dana0.rpy:23
    old "Oh, I'll leave you be then."
    new "Oh, entonces te dejaré en paz."

